                <li>Research Questions
                  <ul>
                    <li>How can we go beyond the barriers? .. Data structures/models... Web standards/stack</li>
                    <li>Operative level: workflows?, processes?.. improving suitable communication interfaces</li>
                    <li>How well can people in the scientific community (progressive/conservation/or even backwards) get their job done.. How usable is it?</li>

                    <li>How can we lift the concepts of articles for scholarly communication</li>
                    <li>How can the workflows in scholarly communication be realised using Web technologies in decentralised manner</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>

                <li>A possible hypothesis is that a lack of an appropriate authentication mechanism impedes adoption of decentralised Web paradigm.</li>

